<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .container {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        padding: 40px;
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .success-icon {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 64px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      h1 {
        color: #10b981;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 28px;
      }

      .subtitle {
        text-align: center;
        color: #666;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .token-section {
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }

      .token-label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 14px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .token-box {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 12px;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        font-size: 12px;
        word-break: break-all;
        color: #495057;
        position: relative;
      }

      .copy-btn {
        position: absolute;
        top: 8px;
        right: 8px;
        background: #4285f4;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 6px 12px;
        font-size: 11px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background 0.3s;
      }

      .copy-btn:hover {
        background: #357ae8;
      }

      .copy-btn:active {
        transform: scale(0.95);
      }

      .info-box {
        background: #e7f3ff;
        border-left: 4px solid #4285f4;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .info-box p {
        color: #1a73e8;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .actions {
        margin-top: 25px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background: #4285f4;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: all 0.3s;
        margin: 0 5px;
      }

      .btn:hover {
        background: #357ae8;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(66, 133, 244, 0.4);
      }

      .btn-secondary {
        background: #6c757d;
      }

      .btn-secondary:hover {
        background: #5a6268;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="success-icon">âœ…</div>
      <h1>Â¡AutenticaciÃ³n Exitosa!</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Has iniciado sesiÃ³n correctamente con Google</p>

      <div class="token-section">
        <div class="token-label">ðŸ”‘ Access Token</div>
        <div class="token-box" id="accessToken">
          <%= accessToken %>
          <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyToken('accessToken')">
            Copiar
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="token-section">
        <div class="token-label">ðŸ”„ Refresh Token</div>
        <div class="token-box" id="refreshToken">
          <%= refreshToken %>
          <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyToken('refreshToken')">
            Copiar
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <p>
          <strong>ðŸ’¡ CÃ³mo usar estos tokens:</strong><br />
          â€¢ <strong>Access Token:</strong> Ãšsalo en el header
          <code>Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;</code> para hacer peticiones
          autenticadas.<br />
          â€¢ <strong>Refresh Token:</strong> Ãšsalo en
          <code>POST /auth/refresh</code> para obtener un nuevo access token
